🔐 Privacy Policy for My School

Effective Date: 28th April 2026

1. Introduction

Welcome to My School.

We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application.

2. Information We Collect

We collect only the information necessary to provide our services.

👤 Personal Information
Name
Phone number
Role (Parent, Teacher, Admin)
Student details (name, class, attendance, etc.)
📱 Usage Data
App usage activity
Device information (for performance and debugging)
📩 Communication Data
Messages, homework, attendance, and notices shared within the app
3. How We Use Your Information

We use your data to:

Provide school-related services (attendance, homework, notices, fees)
Send important notifications
Improve app performance and user experience
Ensure security and prevent misuse
4. Data Sharing

We do NOT sell your data.

We only share data:

With your school administration (relevant to your role)
With trusted service providers (e.g., cloud hosting, notifications)
If required by law
5. Data Storage & Security
Your data is securely stored using cloud services (e.g., Firebase)
We use encryption and access controls to protect your data
Only authorized users (based on roles) can access specific data
6. User Access & Control

You can:

Request access to your data
Request correction of incorrect data
Contact your school/admin for account-related changes
7. Children’s Privacy

My School is designed for use by schools and parents.

Student data is managed by the school
We do not knowingly collect data directly from children without school authorization
8. Notifications

We may send notifications related to:

Attendance
Homework
Fees
School announcements

You can manage notification settings from your device.

9. Third-Party Services

We may use trusted third-party services such as:

Firebase (authentication, database, notifications)
SMS providers (for critical alerts)

These services follow their own privacy policies.

10. Data Retention

We retain data:

As long as your school uses the app
Or as required for legal and operational purposes
11. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.

Users will be notified of significant changes through the app.

